{"tid":1690233,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾馬利：早有預感狼隊會追平","createTime":"2019-11-03T08:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T11:53:55.000Z","uid":165817,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"29235e225d30fdaf28e73be6891a5ae3c0580b35","tid":1690233,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:20:27.000Z","msg":"「我們今天很好地執行了不同的戰術，也很好地保護了球權。我們也曾創造了射入第二球的機會，但始終未能把握住。」<br />\n<br />\n「在遲遲無法擴大領先優勢時，我們就預感到狼隊會扳平。不過總體來說，我們掌握了比賽的節奏，雖然未能取得絕佳機會，但也持續威脅著狼隊大門。」<br />\n<br />\n「比賽結果並不理想，但從戰術上來說，我認為我們成功了，球員們也很拼命。現在是時候放眼下一場了。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有預感會俾人追平，你仲換走個防中托拉拿，換隻新仔翼Saka出嚟做乜撚野？？？？？？？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f6db77e1d2c9e4f0b7dfa844698e907da1ec16ac","tid":1690233,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"買左500K和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />準備退休"},{"pid":"0223c67517326c1cbe2c2af8156d6149b4ea621d","tid":1690233,"uid":199081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T08:28:40.000Z","msg":"個預感係喺馬會投注嗰陣?"},{"pid":"d7cbba926a6fe18c429f3ee35a2cd8bf26981800","tid":1690233,"uid":40588,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"估到會追平 所以換入個翼準備反反cup"},{"pid":"0927d96612f458b715f705ad55b80f2ccbce7ed1","tid":1690233,"uid":282384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:06:26.000Z","msg":"有預感會比人炒"},{"pid":"17887db9206aa9b8a74d5c1ea1a63a11c1d0dbde","tid":1690233,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"掌握比賽節奏？"},{"pid":"703bd5acb18b28b7dd1580347faf0fea931878aa","tid":1690233,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:46:02.000Z","msg":"幾時死"},{"pid":"f89f76e0bd8454292114e1cc00082b5c1b4b18f2","tid":1690233,"uid":165817,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d7cbba926a6fe18c4